des:
Use Alexa to control your Homeable smart devices. You can connect Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download the “Homeable” app in the app store or marketplace and register an account;
(2) Configure your devices in the “Homeable” app and change their names where appropriate;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android or ios app stores and then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “Homeable” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “Homeable” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Homeable” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
